; Based on what I know about Mandarin

; Mandarin has:
; SVO word order
; negation expressed as a preverbal adverb
; yes-no questions with a sentence-final question marker
; 'alternative' or A-not-A questions [don't know how to handle
; these yet]
; simple answers to yes-no questions with V or not V.

; wo3 chi1 fan4
; I eat food
n tv n
*n n tv
*tv n n 

; wo3 bu4 chi1 fan4
; I don't eat  food
n neg-adv tv n
*neg-adv n tv n
*n tv n neg-adv
*n tv neg-adv n

